Pacifix put one hand to his head, concentrating on the internal systems
inside of his military transport half. "My radar is picking up a few
faint signals from inside Slag." He said pointing at the base. Then he
looked upwards, and began in confusion. "I'm also picking up an Autobot
signature." As he then noticed Skyburst. He opened a comm-link to the
helicopter. "Meet us down here, we need to discuss strategy." He asked.
